      • getCanonicalLabels

        public Map<String,List<Map.Entry<String,Long>>> getCanonicalLabels()
        Computes the canonical label for all the sub-graphs that it currently holds. The list of original graphs, after aggregation, is the value of the map entry. Thus it aggregate all canonical sub-graphs together.
        Returns:
        The map from canonically labeled sub-graph to a list of all the representative sub-graphs for that canonical label with the frequency of occurrence.
